    CTRL=$00  INTRQ=clear  DRQ=clear
    Decoded: diskrom=1 romdis=1 intena=0 drive=A side=0
  FDC registers:
    CMD=$00  STATUS=$00  TRK=$00 SEC=$00 DATA=$00 DIR=0
  Drives:
    A: 696320 bytes, 80 tracks, 17 sectors
    B: (unmounted)
```

